oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Mattie Lou - Normal
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Mattie Lou Carroll in the Fall of 1920 at Middle Tennessee State Normal School. The Administration Building, now known as Kirksey Old Main, is in the background. Written beneath the photo: "Mattie Lou - Normal"; written on the back of the photo: "Ever Remember Mattie Lou and the Normal - Will You?"
